name: Jane Addo
description: I am a sweet,romantic woman, I love to play golf I read,love to jogging. I am a good cook. I like to fish and I bait my own hook! I also like to veg out in front of the tv and watch movies sometime. I want to meet someone with some of the same qualities.. I am a great cuddlier. I am good hear-ted woman and want to have fun in life. I am a very loving person and want to be with someone that can actually love in return not just say it but time will tell. I don’t need it but I want it. There is a difference. I am fine with whom I am just want the right one to enhance it. Life is meant to share
